# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# umpatcher.py is a Pygame-based patcher/buffer inspector UI for the UltraMode
# system on Batocera (and related environments). It is intended as a
# controller-first patch browser and buffer inspector.
#
# Core responsibilities:
# - Read a "buffer" (from clipboard, files, logs, or external tools).
# - Classify the buffer content:
#     * Python module
#     * Shell script
#     * Log / output
#     * Notation / AI meta-blocks
#     * Raw patch payload
# - Provide a visual UI (via Pygame) to preview patches before applying.
# - Support multiple patch types:
#     * APPEND
#     * CREATE
#     * FULL (replace entire file)
#     * INSERT_AFTER
#     * INSERT_BEFORE
#     * REPLACE
